reviews.text: A nice place for High Tea.

Good food, good service, around HK$300 each. A bit far if you don't live in the area, few public transport but there is parking spaces. Outdoor sitting and pets are allowed outside. Nice place to have dinner with you furry friend.

Hey ! what’s up food hunters 😎? Wanna eat like a Hongkie(local people)? Let me take u to some Bargain Restaurants for great foods 🍽 ,  i went in this place for lunch , we order a eel fried rice and a pork rack baked with mozzarella , the eel fried rice is average but the pork rack is good meat and fat about 70/30 pork rack is soft well cooked👍🏻, there is no queue when i get here at 12:30 on weekdays , also there r few parking space available , i spend about HK$380 for the lunch, OVERALL - clean & neat ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , food quality ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , atmosphere ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , Bargain $$ ⭐️⭐️out of 5 , price to food quality ratio ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5, if u like my review please hit that LIKE ❤️button thanks and i will see u guys on the next one , love n peace ✌🏻-Detour Guide-

result.adr_address: 香港八鄉石崗上村DD114號
result.name: 金壘餐廳

reviews.text: 遠離市區，需要特意座車去食，食品比之前稍遜
父亲节在这里享用晚餐，是宝贝女儿的主意，点了肉眼扒，燒羊架，加个黑松露鸡肉芝士炒饭。食物质量很好，餐后还有咖啡，值得一赞是咖啡配送的一勺子小奶是熱的，可以看到餐厅服务是无微不至的。
食物質量好，招呼亦好，我會再去。
名牌“紅燒德國豬手”及扒銀雪魚，味絕港九！
午餐出品不錯，招呼細心，休閒一吓，不俗！
